{"type": "article", "id": 31458, "title": "来一场六十分钟的环月旅行｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-25T23:04:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 31994, "name": "Fajno design"}, {"id": 31995, "name": "Stuff"}, {"id": 31996, "name": "Whyd"}, {"id": 31997, "name": "WaterField Designs"}, {"id": 20546, "name": "Richard Yasmine"}, {"id": 31998, "name": "Andrew Neyer"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 71, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160825232725q6fdFX2uyVUsBrw1.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Around the Moon in 60 Minutes by Fajno design</h3><p>想拥有专属于自己的一轮明月？不妨看看这个名为 <a href=\"http://fajnodesign.by/ru/portfolio/around-the-moon-in-60-minutes/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Around the Moon in 60 Minutes</a> 挂钟。来自俄罗斯的设计工作室 <a href=\"http://fajnodesign.by/ru\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fajno design</a> 将环月飞行的舞台搬上了高度还原出月面的钟面，并将分针的一端打造成一艘宇宙飞船，使挂钟看上去充满了探索精神，非常有趣。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232806OgrNCEXytkhGmQDe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.681111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232806vJhwCiNfXZMxul3O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232806B96NSLF0cD1oigjI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232807XGt5iWHDOgyYLEzN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.698889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232806nrxt5MShFHOXQN8j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Whyd by Whyd Inc.</h3><p>拥有语音识别功能的智能家居一度距离我们很遥远，不过现在你的选择已经不仅限于谷歌、亚马逊这样的大公司推出的产品了。今天介绍的这个圆滚滚的音响名叫 <a href=\"https://whyd.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Whyd</a>，内置的五个麦克风可以在五米距离内识别到语音命令，无论是暂停、切换曲目还是歌名和自定义歌单都不在话下。除此之外，用户还能够通过顶部的触控区进行操作。它的外观看上去相当简洁，使用时隐藏在隔栅下方的 RGB LCD 显示屏会根据当前播放状态浮现出不同的图标。这是它的<a href=\"https://whyd.com/checkout/\" rel=\"nofollow\">预定链接</a>，售价为 299 美元，计划于 2017 年初发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825233000m6yR2jxCOrHB7X9h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608252330000eNfGzvabUPh7LEA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825233001ntKVBvgIOj8MeR2c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.774167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608252330014y9gaUGkPDTAiExZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825233001HdONazv2lCDZ1EjM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825233000w6jI2UhnbcAT8oM5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Clou by Richard Yasmine</h3><p>来自黎巴嫩的建筑师和产品设计师 <a href=\"http://www.richardyasmine.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Richard Yasmine</a> 将在九月初举行的巴黎时尚家居设计展（<a href=\"http://www.maison-objet.com/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maison et Object</a>）秋展上展出这款名为 Clou 的边桌。它的立柱成角锥状，与正中央有一道凹槽的桌面相连，单独放在地上时就像是一个放大版的钉子。Yasmine 在设计时也还原了钉子的特性，只有将它“钉”入配套的底座才能组合出一张完整的边桌。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232932n94QowBuMSDAqrVX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608252329327TK8WfynEmlGu21V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608252329325KBauw3WpYMxzfcS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608252329333a69SFeBCjxt0bEq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232933VTIk3P8wdirp2mAR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232932ErjZH7MdmnsQvB4i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cactus Catchall by Stuff</h3><p>由美国设计师 Andrew Neyer 成立的家居品牌 <a href=\"https://andrewneyer.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stuff</a> 最近以三种不同形状的仙人掌为原型，设计了一组名为 Cactus Catchall 的金属收纳架。架子上细密的挂钩就像是一根根仙人掌刺一样，可以挂上帽子、背包或是其他小物，让室内的环境变得生动不少。这是它的<a href=\"https://andrewneyer.com/product/cactus-catchall/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价分别为 199、275 和 500 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232918nFki7DQv4pe3AxPX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608252329195BrYbPCea6G8sVDc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232919fbHoyNwDIi4Fs5K6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232920UQD3j2JmNilwBAaY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lift by Levitation Works</h3><p>想换个姿势为你的智能手表充电？这款由 <a href=\"http://www.levitationworks.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Levitation Works</a> 研发的无线充电器 Lift 不仅可以为 Pebble 或是 Apple Watch 提供悬浮式充电，当你把智能手机放在底座上它也会自动为设备进行无线充电。如果你没有智能手表的话，Lift 同时也可以当做智能灯具使用，只要将配套的 Orb 放在底座上，它就会自动悬浮起来，只要轻轻摁下头部的开关就可以点亮。由于 Orb 采用内置式电池，当你充满电后还可以利用底部的磁性将它放置在任何金属表面上。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1465703413/lift-anti-gravity-levitating-smartwatch-charger\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 149 美元，包含 Orb 智能灯的套装早鸟价为 219 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232859JOzUxloEKsCcgZ32.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232900E3KIDWQzXqJPwc0F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232859AUEdQuOBy3on8H2g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232900LD8NsPZ27eItbH5E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232859RDP3NdjvOiwzKV9p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.428333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Intrepid iPhone Travel Wallet by WaterField Designs</h3><p>出行时又是手机又是钱包、护照等随身物品是不是有时觉得两只手都不够用？旧金山配件品牌 <a href=\"http://www.sfbags.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">WaterField Designs</a> 最近推出了一款名为 Intrepid 的旅行钱包，目前在 Kickstarter 上已经筹集到了目标额八倍多的资金，可见大家对这一旅行小烦恼还挺有共鸣的。从功能上看，它像是智能手机壳与钱包的结合：将手机放进钱包内专用的夹层后，你就可以通过正面的遮板像平时一样流畅地操作手机。除了手机之外，Intrepid 还可以容纳护照、笔、现金、各类卡片以及一个附赠的零钱包，非常实用。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/waterfielddesigns/the-intrepid-travel-wallet-for-iphone-7-made-in-us\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价为 79 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232830Eoa5JrUixP3KjmzL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232830B3hr6LnxVKwZWUT8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232830CWxS06zrkBTlOahA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.466863\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232830PcZ6B3dXQTfRF0Na.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.222059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160825232830Ky1sNvSkouwIAMtT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}